com.kamomileware.maven.plugin.opencms

Class AbstractModuleMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • com.kamomileware.maven.plugin.opencms.AbstractModuleMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModuleMojo

    public abstract class AbstractModuleMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Base class for opencms-module maven plugin mojos. Contains references to maven components and configurations.
    Author:
    jagarcia
